{"id":539807,"date":[{"year":1974,"month":10,"day":28}],"page":"4","source":"新华社","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"442","ytitle":"","mtitle":"南海诸岛之一——西沙群岛","ftitle":"摄影展览作品选","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\10\\74as040101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>伍振超</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>重任在肩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在西沙自卫反击作战中荣立一等功的广东省南海水产公司四○七号渔轮鱼捞员、共青团员潘正安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伍振超　摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\10\\74as040102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>保卫领空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西沙永兴岛民兵高射炮连的同志们在进行对空射击训练。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伍振超　摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\10\\74as040103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>杨明辉</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>座落在西沙群岛永兴岛上的广东省西沙群岛、南沙群岛、中沙群岛革命委员会办公大楼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨明辉　摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\10\\74as040104.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>中央领导同志赠送给西沙军民的毛主席著作在连队颁发(金银岛)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伍振超　摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\10\\74as040105.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>伙伴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海军某舰三七炮炮长田忠槐在西沙自卫反击作战中，满怀对敌人的刻骨仇恨，沉着果断地指挥火炮，狠狠地打击敌人，荣立一等功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伍振超　摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\10\\74as040106.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>黄旌整</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>西沙女民兵(永兴岛)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄旌整　摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\10\\74as040107.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>能文能武(珊瑚岛)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在西沙自卫反击作战中荣立集体二等功的某部两栖侦察队指战员在阵地上办起批林批孔专栏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伍振超　摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\10\\74as040108.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>黄旌整</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>一声令下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西沙永兴岛上的女民兵在进行实战演习·"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄旌整　摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\10\\74as040109.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>任明福</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>西沙雄鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空军某部飞行员警惕地巡航在祖国的西沙群岛上空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任明福　摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\10\\74as040110.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>冯大广</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>建设中的西沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西沙珊瑚岛上的军民在紧张地施工。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯大广　摄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(本版照片均新华社发)</FONT>"}]}